This is developed by Dev. Shyam For Docker demonstration purpose only....@Unique-Force 
--DATE : "null"
Modules:

nitro-app -> API
vue-app -> CLIENT 


.... Lets spin up the server 
1. docker-compose -p docker-demo build --no-cache 
2. docker-compose up

// Use with caution because this will remove the running containers 
1. docker-compose down

// Instead Run this..
1. docker-compose start
2. docker-compose stop


// To start individually 
1. docker start docker-demo-api-1 docker-demo-web-1

// To stop individually
1. docker stop docker-demo-api-1 docker-demo-web-1


3. docker-compose exec api cat /etc/os-release  ||  docker-compose exec web cat /etc/os-release
